⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Dr. Brodsky
node ACO · ACO · ⟦Dr. Brodsky:ACO:a4b9b0⟧

WHO   — Dr. Brodsky — the conditioner
WHAT  — The technician of the cure: efficient, incurious about the soul, indifferent that the conditioning also destroys Alex's love of music.
WHERE — ACO · A CLOCKWORK ORANGE  Framework inputs: A Clockwork Orange (Anthony Burgess, 1962)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the warning needs the banal expert who executes the remaking without asking what it costs.
HOW   — By nausea-inducing drugs and films of violence (scored, fatefully, with Beethoven), repeated until the reflex is set.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I make violence physically unbearable to you — and if your beloved Ninth Symphony gets caught in the same reflex, that is a side-effect, not my concern.

